ate appendage; lateral lobes ovate to triangular, deflexed, gibbous, dark brown­ ish-hairy; speculum scutelliform, annular or H-shaped, large, violet or blue with yellow or whitish margin, the spots often somewhat dark brownish-velutinous with glabrous margin. Connective acute.",GBIF,"PlantNet species_id: 165
