since been obscured by widespread introduction and cultivation since ancient times to the present day. It is now naturalised across much of the world with temperate climates.",https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papaver_somniferum,https://powo.science.kew.org/results?q=Papaver+somniferum,"6. Papaver calycibus capsulisque glabris, foliis amplexicaulibus incisis. Papaver caule multifloro, foliis simplicibus glabris incisis caulinis. Hort. ups. 135. Mat. med. 250. Papaver foliis simplicibus glabris incisis. Hort. cliff. 200. Hall. helv. 303. Roy. lugdb. 879. Papaver hortense, semine albo. Bauh. pin. 170. β. Papaver hortense, semine nigro. Bauh. pin. 170. γ. Papaver cristatum, floribus & semine album. Bauh. pin. 171. δ. Papaver cristatum, floribus rubris, semine nigro. Bauh. pin. 171. ε. Papaver, flore pleno, album. Bauh. pin. 171.",GBIF,"PlantNet species_id: 202
