GBIF description: Note: El-Gadi (in Jafri & El-Gadi, Fl. Libya 57: 77. 1978) indicated 1182.1 (LINN) as type, but this is a Kaehler collection, not received by Linnaeus until 1757 and not, therefore, original material for the name. Cowley (in Polhill, Fl. Trop. E. Africa, Smilacaceae: 2. 1989) indicated Clifford material as the type but did not distinguish between the two sheets preserved there; she made a definitive choice in 1993.
