Wikipedia summary: The Giardino Montano Linasia is a nature preserve and botanical garden located at 720 meters altitude near Monte Linas in San Benedetto, Iglesias, Province of Carbonia-Iglesias, Sardinia, Italy. Opening days depend on the time of year; an admission fee is charged.
Distribution: Austria (INTRODUCED); Corse; Sardegna; Global (PRESENT); Germany [I]; Corsica; Sardinia; FR
