f overlap some hybrids have been observed, which are distinguishable by intermediate flower morphology. In the 1930s a hybrid was also developed for horticultural purposes.",https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptostegia_madagascariensis,https://powo.science.kew.org/results?q=Cryptostegia+madagascariensis,Amazonia | Caribe | Pacifico,GBIF,"PlantNet species_id: 620
