a_aculeata,https://powo.science.kew.org/results?q=Pereskia+aculeata,"Lectotype (Wijnands, Bot. Commelins: 58. 1983): [icon] "" Pereskia aculeata, flore albo, fructu flavescente Plumier "" in Dillenius, Hort. Eltham. 2: 305, t. 227, f. 294. 1732.",GBIF,"PlantNet species_id: 672
